<p class="max-w-3xl mx-auto font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-primary-container/90 mb-12">
                Maximiza tu retorno de inversión (ROI) y atrae prospectos altamente calificados con estrategias probadas en Google Ads, Meta Ads y TikTok.
            </p>
<div class="relative w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-12 transform hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-700">
<img alt="Hero Background" class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-2xl border border-on-primary-container/20" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuD0OVxv2uytxwUYZ0xjmP7YB1G272Io0p0z9HX5ao233PhA_v9SlMgwDXO25Q1cxD82N0xDc1K1IKxIBaARKckCfrrhXZBhQVUVhCz2VpYxLPZqtqxecG6WZAZQZqaZ2vOmUvdLtXW_RH8mk5X0-VbMVsjeyi9Hnq20GqiF8aj8PPJ3Doq3Ai5Gci_cLjhcVdJx2FKi5kzFSQ_1gtfNn5_Zds_p7fnu-DuLlhRFdvzUwvGzzue3uNIjBf_zRead1UZ9i_2PeQhQTW9S"/>
